       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. MAIN.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 STAGE-LEFT PIC S9(9).
       01 STAGE-RIGHT PIC S9(9).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN.
           CALL 'SHOWCASE-TEXT'.
           CALL 'PRINT-STAGE'.
           COMPUTE STAGE-LEFT = 19.
           COMPUTE STAGE-RIGHT = 23.
           CALL 'PRINT-STAGE-TOTAL' USING BY REFERENCE STAGE-LEFT BY REFERENCE STAGE-RIGHT.
           CALL 'SHOWCASE-SNAPSHOT'.
           CALL 'SHOWCASE-PORTFOLIO'.
           CALL 'SHOWCASE-MEMORY'.
           DISPLAY "FEATURE SHOWCASE COMPLETE".
           STOP RUN.

       END PROGRAM MAIN.

